{"tid":2202370,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[想搵番一個老師] 希望各位幫幫手 入黎睇下","createTime":"2020-09-14T13:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T15:19:12.000Z","uid":375706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c7137649d68fbad642653b333d763cda370fc9","tid":2202370,"uid":375706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"第一次開post🙏🏻<br />\n有咩講錯 請多多包涵🙏🏻🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n我想搵番一個小一班主任<br />\n但由於我冇乜關於佢既資料<br />\n所以希望可以借助到各位既力量<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmVqYkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmVqYkC.jpg&h=e8da56e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢係圖中左手面果位老師<br />\n我只係知道佢姓丁<br />\n佢係我2003-2004學年小一班主任<br />\n我記得佢主要係教英文<br />\n<br />\n我想搵番佢係因為幾個月前發夢夢見佢<br />\n我已經唔記得咗夢嘅內容<br />\n但醒咗之後好想見番佢<br />\n我有試過google同facebook搵佢<br />\n但無奈我冇佢全名<br />\n所以都係得個吉<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢教我嘅時候我仲係好細個<br />\n但我好記得佢係一個好好嘅老師<br />\n所以想知道佢過成點<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫下眼🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙏🏻"},{"pid":"1398b1f75a7c2a6ab5368e497bc61bc209819b19","tid":2202370,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:42:27.000Z","msg":"邊個係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e69ea6b3e734626b943ac634b6855486b1839fc","tid":2202370,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"好似blur下啲細蚊仔個頭好啲wor"},{"pid":"e6d437123d89afc554bc5a9f23d7e528645d32c5","tid":2202370,"uid":375706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e69ea6b3e734626b943ac634b6855486b1839fc","tid":2202370,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"好似blur下啲細蚊仔個頭好啲wor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:49:10.000Z","msg":"My bad🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\nUpload張近少少既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOZOWcw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOZOWcw.png&h=53feac80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"203e0ab398e9